:{{A|VO chapter2 2 mar7th 114.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Excuse me, any chance you saw a foxian lady pass by?
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 awang 101.ogg}} '''Forth:''' Well that's a heck of a question, miss! I'd say nearly one in every two people passing through Starskiff Haven is foxian. We might have seen the lady you're looking for, but we wouldn't have batted an eyelid.
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 alai 101.ogg}} '''Back'n:''' He's not lying. Still, if you describe her a little, maybe it'll jog our memory.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} She's... foxian?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102050706-->
::{{A|VO chapter2 2 awang 102.ogg}} '''Forth:''' Write that down, write that down!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} She's... pretty.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102050708-->
::{{A|VO chapter2 2 awang 103.ogg}} '''Forth:''' "Pretty?" That's too generic for a foxian. Even if you don't count the ladies, there are plenty of gents that fit that description like a glove...
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_102050709-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102050709-->
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 alai 102.ogg}} '''Back'n:''' As tedious as it is, I'm afraid you'll have to describe her in more detail. Please don't say "two ears, one tail."
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Show Tingyun's photo.)
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102050711-->
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 awang 104.ogg}} '''Forth:''' ...I can put my hand on my heart and say I remember this fine lady.
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 alai 103.ogg}} '''Back'n:''' Nonsense. I've been stood next to you this whole time and I don't remember anyone like her.
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 awang 105.ogg}} '''Forth:''' Well, I may not have seen her in person, but her beauty feels like a long-lost acquaintance... How wonderful to be reunited with her after so long!
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 alai 104 m.ogg}} {{A|VO chapter2 2 alai 104 f.ogg}} '''Back'n:''' Oh dear. I'm sorry, my friend here appears to have lost touch with reality.
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 mar7th 115.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Are you two professional time-wasters or something?
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 awang 106.ogg}} '''Forth:''' Please accept our apologies! Me and my partner do double act comedy in the Sleepless Earl &mdash; the teahouse round the corner. As you can probably guess, with all these curfews and lockdowns, we've hardly had an audience the past few days. We figured we'd find a spot on the street and do some rehearsal &mdash; just to stop us getting rusty.
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 alai 105.ogg}} '''Back'n:''' Then you guys swung by asking for this foxian lady, so we thought we'd give you a bit of improv &mdash; free of charge I might add.
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 awang 107.ogg}} '''Forth:''' Stay calm, stay calm! I did see the girl you're looking for. She took a turn from here into Starwatcher Avenue. I'd suggest you head over that way &mdash; she might still be there.
:{{A|VO chapter2 2 mar7th 116.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' I find it hard to trust anything you've just said...
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Mission_102050107_01-->
:'''Forth:''' I can give something worth a bit more than that.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502011002_55-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502011002_55-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} I'd like to hear another skit.
