::'''Forth:''' You can't talk about Starskiff Haven without mentioning the Palace of Astrum, and you can't talk about the Palace of Astrum without mentioning Madam Yukong.
::'''Back'n:''' I once saw Madam Yukong with her Cloudkite Resplendent Longbow, shooting with tremendous accuracy from a hundred feet away. Truly a sight to&mdash;
::'''Forth:''' Hang on, "a hundred feet"? Are you saying if I stood 101 feet away, I could just pluck her arrows out of the air?
::'''Back'n:''' It's a figure of speech. Generally speaking, Madam Yukong's arrows are a threat from even 5000 feet.
::'''Forth:''' So you're saying if I stood 5001 feet away, I could catch her arrows.
::'''Back'n:''' *Xianzhou profanity* &mdash; why do you have to catch her arrows???
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Are you guys practicing your crosstalk here?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502110110-->
::'''Forth:''' Hi! We're both port workers, so we just come here to practice whenever we find the time. It's not really convenient elsewhere.
::'''Back'n:''' We're usually really busy and can never find the time. Luckily, the port is close by, so we can squeeze in some practice. It's the kind of thing you get better at by practicing.
::'''Forth:''' Speaking of which, Mr. Xiyan over at the Sleepless Earl is a fan of ours, so we sometimes perform a few skits at the teahouse. We don't earn much money, but the experience is priceless.
::'''Back'n:''' We are gonna head to some bigger stages for our skits in the future. Right, my bro?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You guys are gonna be stars in the future.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} The artist's path is long and difficult.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502110116-->
::'''Forth:''' Then I'll have to give you an autograph while I can. Who knows how much it'll be worth in the future?
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I'll come back next time.
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
