::<!--Trigger PerformanceD 800324602: Config/Level/Mission/8003246/Act/Act800324602.json-->
::'''Back'n:''' Alas, looks like our audience has some other ideas today.
::'''Forth:''' Come on, it's one thing to joke about others and a whole different thing to joke about our audience. If we do that, we'll end up becoming the joke in this business.
::'''Back'n:''' Yeah, you laugh at your customer...
::'''Forth:''' And you end up a bummer!
::'''Back'n:''' You make an ill-timed joke...
::'''Forth:''' And you'll be broke! Wait, wait, we're not making terrible jokes. We're straying from the point, so let's get back to the folks!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How about I record the crosstalk improv you just had?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813246030-->
:::'''Back'n:''' Nah, forget it. It's terrible, not catchy at all.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Can you guys give me a definite answer?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813246032-->
:::'''Back'n:''' Not so fast. We'll have to talk about it.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Now your audience wants a "yes" answer...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813246034-->
:::'''Back'n:''' Don't worry. We were just improvising, and you'll get an answer from us soon.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_813246035-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813246035-->
::'''Back'n:''' There's still much room for our improvisation, but let's put it on hold for now. The recording thing sounds good to me, but I need my partner's opinion before making a final decision.
::'''Forth:''' Well... I'm not sure about that...
::'''Back'n:''' But why not? It's just doing our regular customer a favor, right? A flat-out rejection will make us seem heartless.
::'''Forth:''' It's not like I want to reject your request outright, but Back'n and I are just crosstalk lovers. We don't have enough experience to put on a great show yet.
::'''Back'n:''' We've put on a few decent shows, but that's all about it. To be frank, we've had fewer successful performances than the coins in my pocket.
::'''Forth:''' I just can't guarantee that our crosstalk comedy will really attract any customers for Tall Auntie's stall in Aurum Alley.
::'''Forth:''' Yeah, we might be older than you, but we don't have much more experience in crosstalk performance. We just don't want to leave any negative impressions on our potential audience.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why don't you guys do live performances instead?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813246043-->
:::'''Back'n:''' Because we simply don't have the time. We're just crosstalk lovers, and we've got work to do at the dock on work days.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Don't worry. You will be generously paid.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813246045-->
:::'''Forth:''' Hah, do we look like we are solely motivated by money? We've got our own jobs to do.
:::'''Back'n:''' I've known him since I was a kid, and I know him well. He gets into the crosstalk industry for fun, and he doesn't really expect us to hit it big with our performances.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I think you guys are overthinking things...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813246048-->
:::'''Forth:''' As newcomers in this industry, we can't be too careful with our new career.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_813246049-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813246049-->
::'''Forth:''' Yeah, please understand our concerns and don't make things too difficult for us.
::'''Back'n:''' Please don't bring up the recording thing again, but if you ever want to listen to our crosstalk, you're always welcome here.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_800324602-->
